(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ (U ⇒ V) = no (λ ())
(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ never = no (λ ())
(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ unknown = no (λ ())
(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ number = no (λ ())
(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ boolean = no (λ ())
(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ (U ∪ V) with (S ≡ᵀ U) | (T ≡ᵀ V) 
(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ (S ∪ T) | yes refl | yes refl = yes refl
(S ∪ T) ≡ᵀ (U ∪ V) | _ | no p = no (λ q → p (cong rhs q))
